stand it anymore.

14:01.808 --> 14:05.109
I run over to her,
grab her by the shoulders.

14:05.111 --> 14:07.278
I look her in the eye.
I say: [ Retching Continues ]

14:07.280 --> 14:11.783
"Miss Stevie.
I'm nobody, but I'm a fan.

14:11.785 --> 14:15.386
And there's a lot of kids
out there tonight just like me...

14:15.388 --> 14:19.891
fans, who saved all month
to come and hear Stevie Nicks sing.

14:19.893 --> 14:22.427
To see Stevie Nicks twirl."

14:23.530 --> 14:25.029
What happened?

14:25.031 --> 14:28.399
Yeah. Crazy.
She head-butted me.

14:29.302 --> 14:31.703
Deviated septum...
that I still have.

14:31.705 --> 14:33.404
[ Sniffs ]

14:33.406 --> 14:36.641
Blood everywhere,
all over both of us.

14:36.643 --> 14:41.880
