that stupid cover shit.

37:57.042 --> 37:58.541
Creative suicide.

37:58.543 --> 38:02.912
"A"... It's called
"management strategy."

38:02.914 --> 38:04.981
And two...

38:04.983 --> 38:08.585
Why don't you get me my passport
and wallet back for the $1,000?

38:08.587 --> 38:11.154
How about if I punch a hole
through your heart right now?

38:11.156 --> 38:12.989
Get out of my way.

38:14.226 --> 38:15.959
Twenty-four hours!

38:19.097 --> 38:20.697
One day.

38:21.600 --> 38:24.301
You're repeating yourself.

38:24.303 --> 38:25.735
[ Shower Running ]

38:25.737 --> 38:28.438
[ Richie ]
♪ Come down off your throne ♪

38:28.440 --> 38:32.475
♪ And leave your body alone ♪

38:32.477 --> 38:38.014
♪ You are the reason
I've been waiting so long ♪

38:40.118 --> 38:45.422
♪ Somebody holds the key ♪

38:46.925 --> 38:50.660
♪ But I'm near the end ♪

38:50.662 --> 38:57.200
♪ And I just
ain't got the time ♪

38:57.202 --> 38:58.935
♪ And I'm wasted ♪

38:58.937 --> 39:02.939
♪ And I can't
find my way home ♪♪

39:02.941 --> 39:04.474
It's ridiculous! Woodstock...

39:04.476 --> 39:06.943
Jimi Hendrix played
<i>The Star Spangled Banner...</i>

39:06.945 --> 39:09.512
because I asked him to!

39:11.283 --> 39:13.683
Two weeks...

39:13.685 --> 39:16.152
to get a passport
to my own country.

39:16.154 --> 39:18.288
<i>[ Radio: Pop ]</i>
Hey...

39:18.290 --> 39:22.492
Could you please turn down
the "Boogie Oogie Oogie Oogie"?

39:22.494 --> 39:24.794
<i>♪♪ [ Stops ]</i>
Hey, boss. How about lunch?

39:24.796 --> 39:26.396
Do you like Mexican?

39:27.299 --> 39:29.199
Mexican's fine.

39:29.201 --> 39:30.900
But no food.

39:30.902 --> 39:35.004
Madonna?
Please. Donna.

39:35.006 --> 39:38.842
Donna Elaine Beckerman.
Grosse Pointe, Michigan.

39:38.844 --> 39:41.745
- I gave her the name Madonna.
- That's why you are a very famous man.

39:41.747 --> 39:44.981
- Saw her singing on the street.
- Yes. The Hamburger Hamlet.

39:44.983 --> 39:46.549
On Sunset.

39:47.319 --> 39:48.918
Legendary ears.

39:50.389 --> 39:52.422
Oh. Mr. Richie.

39:53.992 --> 39:56.326
Tonight is <i> Afghan Star.</i>

39:56.328 --> 39:58.061
On TV.

39:58.063 --> 40:00.230
<i>[ TV: Man Speaking Dari ]</i>

40:00.232 --> 40:02.565
<i>Afghan Star?</i>
Yes. Big TV show.

40:02.567 --> 40:05.502
Like your <i> American Idol.</i>

40:05.504 --> 40:07.270
Huge competition
for our singers.

40:07.272 --> 40:09.439
He is favorite.

40:10.842 --> 40:15.211
All of Afghanistan,
they watch it and they vote it.

40:15.213 --> 40:17.514
For money?
Yes, of course.

40:17.516 --> 40:22.118
Winner gets $5,000 American
and record deal.

40:23.121 --> 40:25.588
I dig the suit. Retro.

40:25.590 --> 40:29.092
Hey. Uncle Rich, we've got to get out of here.
We've got something better than this.

40:29.094 --> 40:31.928
It's there! It's there!
Whoa!

40:32.697 --> 40:34.364
Whoa! Look at that, huh?

40:34.366 --> 40:36.966
Three months I've been trying to get
that fucking thing to spiral.

40:40.238 --> 40:41.871
Here you go.

40:43.708 --> 40:47.010
- What's that for?
- That's some gangster shit.

40:48.146 --> 40:49.979
Just consider it a lifetime
achievement award.

40:49.981 --> 40:51.915
Look, I think what
he's trying to say...

40:51.917 --> 40:56.219
is that, ultimately, you are our arms man,
and you are in trouble.

40:56.221 --> 40:58.054
That's about $15,000.

40:58.056 --> 40:59.989
Not enough?

41:07.732 --> 41:10.400
- What do you guys want?
- Fucking mind reader.

41:10.402 --> 41:11.468
Clairvoyant.

41:11.470 --> 41:13.002
Okay, what we're looking for...

41:13.004 --> 41:15.405
