01:08:25.868 --> 01:08:27.801
He's very good.

01:08:27.804 --> 01:08:30.772
[ Speaking In Dari ]

01:08:35.879 --> 01:08:37.412
[ Applause ]
Okay.

01:08:37.413 --> 01:08:39.493
Now's a good time
to be sick.

01:08:47.557 --> 01:08:50.358
