She was really something.

01:12:19.102 --> 01:12:22.837
<i>♪ What else can a poor boy do? ♪</i>

01:12:28.778 --> 01:12:32.113
May I hide from the wind
over here?

01:12:32.115 --> 01:12:34.282
[ Chuckles ]

01:12:34.284 --> 01:12:36.417
<i>♪♪ [ Continues ]</i>

01:12:39.723 --> 01:12:43.358
<i>[ Male Reporter Speaking Dari ]</i>

01:13:08.485 --> 01:13:10.551
