she could have won it all!

01:13:36.346 --> 01:13:39.414
We could have won it all, Dad.

01:13:54.297 --> 01:13:55.963
[ Tariq Speaks Pashto ]

01:14:09.579 --> 01:14:11.746
[ Daoud ] If she goes back
to the village, Richie,

01:14:11.748 --> 01:14:14.615
