from the ballot.

01:14:24.260 --> 01:14:26.461
[ Richie ]
What a beautiful picture.

01:14:27.497 --> 01:14:29.063
Miss, would you mind moving?

01:14:29.065 --> 01:14:31.299
I'm trying to look at the skyline here.
Thank you.

01:14:31.301 --> 01:14:33.267
Asshole.

01:14:33.269 --> 01:14:35.136
What time is your flight?

01:14:38.608 --> 01:14:42.109
8:00 to Dubai.
Three-hour layover.

01:14:42.111 --> 01:14:46.514
And then I got a direct flight to LA.
Gotta sleep.

01:14:48.751 --> 01:14:50.485
I was going to tell you.
Really.

01:14:50.487 --> 01:14:52.920
When it comes to men,
I'm usually two steps ahead.

01:14:52.922 --> 01:14:55.523
[ Richie ] It wasn't supposed
to end this way.

01:14:55.525 --> 01:14:57.625
That girl has talent.

01:14:57.627 --> 01:15:01.429
She has the gift.
She has the magic. I know it.

01:15:01.431 --> 01:15:04.499
How the hell good am I
if I can't break a talent like that?

01:15:04.501 --> 01:15:06.467
Honey, I saw the audience.

01:15:06.469 --> 01:15:10.204
They did not dig
an uncovered Pashtun girl...

01:15:10.206 --> 01:15:12.039
singing Cat Stevens in English.

01:15:13.943 --> 01:15:15.676
Sweetness and light.

01:15:16.312 --> 01:15:18.112
I watched that crowd.

01:15:18.114 --> 01:15:20.348
They wanted to go with her.

01:15:20.350 --> 01:15:21.949
They were dying to go with her.

01:15:21.951 --> 01:15:25.620
They just weren't able
to go with her because it was in public.

01:15:25.622 --> 01:15:27.221
You really believe that?

01:15:27.223 --> 01:15:29.123
I sure do.

01:15:30.159 --> 01:15:31.893
So?
So...

01:15:31.895 --> 01:15:35.029
daddy bear took her
out of the show, and she quit.

01:15:35.031 --> 01:15:39.867
Quit? You quit. It was that easy
for you to walk away.

01:15:39.869 --> 01:15:45.740
First little bump in the road,
and Mr. Richie's just giving up,

01:15:45.742 --> 01:15:50.077
slinking back to his
little Van Nuys world.

01:15:50.079 --> 01:15:53.147
I don't think you know
quite what you're talking about.

01:15:53.149 --> 01:15:55.816
Nah. I don't know shit.

01:15:55.818 --> 01:15:58.553
I know, 'cause my daddy
told me that.

01:15:59.689 --> 01:16:01.889
"Merci, just shut up.
Put on a tube top.

01:16:01.891 --> 01:16:04.992
Go find yourself a rich man
while you still can."

01:16:06.095 --> 01:16:10.364
And for a long time, too long,
I believed him.

01:16:10.366 --> 01:16:12.400
But you know what,
Richie?

01:16:12.402 --> 01:16:15.002
I am not dumb.

01:16:15.004 --> 01:16:18.539
I'm gonna walk out of here
with a serious nest egg...

01:16:18.541 --> 01:16:22.276
and open my own
real estate agency in Oahu.

01:16:24.380 --> 01:16:26.180
Richie Lanz,
I fought to be a winner,

01:16:26.182 --> 01:16:31.586
and I do not have time
for quitters and losers.

01:16:31.588 --> 01:16:34.589
I am not a loser.

01:16:34.591 --> 01:16:37.191
I am a quitter.

01:16:37.193 --> 01:16:39.627
If you really know talent,

01:16:39.629 --> 01:16:45.032
and you really know that Salima's
gonna win her way into the next round,

01:16:45.034 --> 01:16:46.767
then do something.

01:16:46.769 --> 01:16:49.236
Figure something out, man.
I don't know.

01:16:49.238 --> 01:16:50.938
But win, goddamn it.

01:16:52.208 --> 01:16:56.477
God, you are really crazy about me,
aren't you?

01:16:56.479 --> 01:17:00.982
I am your partner with this girl,
but I bet on you, Richie.

01:17:00.984 --> 01:17:03.050
Not her. You.

01:17:03.052 --> 01:17:05.953
And you better
deliver me my 30%.

01:17:12.161 --> 01:17:14.095
I got an idea.

01:17:14.097 --> 01:17:16.297
Of course you do, hon.

01:17:18.735 --> 01:17:20.635
It's a million-to-one shot.

01:17:23.006 --> 01:17:27.208
But so...
were the Bay City Rollers.

01:17:52.468 --> 01:17:54.935
Hey.<i> As-salaam alaikum.</i>

01:17:55.605 --> 01:17:57.104
<i>Alaikum salaam.</i>

01:18:01.210 --> 01:18:04.912
What do you say we keep
Salima on the ballot?

01:18:06.215 --> 01:18:07.715
What?

01:18:07.717 --> 01:18:12.319
Well, who actually knows that she quit?
I mean, officially.

01:18:12.321 --> 01:18:15.122
I know.
My staff knows.

01:18:15.124 --> 01:18:17.858
Okay, but they don't know,
right?

01:18:20.530 --> 01:18:22.463
On TV last night...

01:18:22.465 --> 01:18:26.467
there was her name on the ballot
with a phone number to call. Yes.

01:18:26.469 --> 01:18:31.005
You know, if you haven't officially
removed her from the ballot, don't.

01:18:31.007 --> 01:18:34.008
She's risked her life.
Come on.

01:18:34.010 --> 01:18:37.011
It'd be great for her village,
for her family, for her people,

01:18:37.013 --> 01:18:40.381
the nation, the world,
women everywhere.

01:18:40.383 --> 01:18:42.750
Maybe.
You know, probably.

01:18:42.752 --> 01:18:45.486
But I found this girl in a cave.

01:18:45.488 --> 01:18:49.090
And I heard her, and...

01:18:50.426 --> 01:18:52.426
I just got to know, man.

01:18:53.896 --> 01:18:56.330
I just got to know.

01:18:56.332 --> 01:18:58.399
And don't you wanna know?

01:19:03.673 --> 01:19:05.673
I already know.

01:19:05.675 --> 01:19:09.343
This conversation
never happened, okay?

01:19:14.517 --> 01:19:16.517
Salima!

01:19:16.519 --> 01:19:18.252
Salima!

01:19:18.254 --> 01:19:19.420
Salima!

01:19:23.192 --> 01:19:25.359
<i>♪♪ [ Woman Singing
In Foreign Language ]</i>

01:19:40.443 --> 01:19:43.110
<i>♪♪ [ Continues ]</i>

01:19:55.391 --> 01:19:57.458
[ Shouting ]

01:19:59.262 --> 01:20:02.797
[ Horns Honking ]

01:20:10.840 --> 01:20:14.842
[ Speaking Pashto ]

01:20:18.748 --> 01:20:20.815
<i>[ Daoud Speaking Dari ]</i>

01:20:27.957 --> 01:20:31.158
You okay? Oh, I think
I'm bleeding somewhere.

01:20:57.186 --> 01:21:00.054
I am going to brain this guy.

01:21:00.056 --> 01:21:02.690
Salima Khan! Salima Khan!

01:21:02.692 --> 01:21:07.361
[ Cheering ]

01:21:07.363 --> 01:21:09.496
[ Gunshots ]

01:21:09.498 --> 01:21:11.866
[ Tariq Shouting In Pashto ]

01:21:25.314 --> 01:21:26.647
Salima Khan!

01:21:26.649 --> 01:21:28.883
<i>Salima Khan!</i>

01:21:28.885 --> 01:21:31.085
<i>[ Fades ]
Salima Khan!</i>

01:21:34.724 --> 01:21:36.423
Salima Khan!

01:21:36.425 --> 01:21:39.059
Salima Khan! Salima Khan!

01:21:39.061 --> 01:21:42.963
She did it! You did it!
We're in!

01:21:45.534 --> 01:21:47.034
What?

01:21:47.036 --> 01:21:50.537
Salima Khan! Salima Khan!

01:21:50.539 --> 01:21:56.076
<i>Salima Khan!
♪♪ [ Woman Vocalizing ]</i>

01:22:06.722 --> 01:22:11.191
Technically, the daddy
did threaten to cut off my head.

01:22:11.193 --> 01:22:15.129
That was before his lambkin
made it to the final round.

01:22:15.131 --> 01:22:17.598
Hey, he will put your head
on a spike.

01:22:17.600 --> 01:22:20.134
Come on. Babe, please.

01:22:21.037 --> 01:22:23.203
Face-to-face? I own him.

01:22:26.142 --> 01:22:29.376
Everything all right?
I have to go to work.

01:22:29.378 --> 01:22:30.644
Work?

01:22:33.983 --> 01:22:36.050
But you said that you retired.

01:22:36.052 --> 01:22:38.552
You-You said
you discovered Madonna.

01:22:40.056 --> 01:22:43.123
I don't have a choice.
None.

01:22:43.125 --> 01:22:45.693
So you're just gonna have to
trust me on this, Richie.

01:22:46.462 --> 01:22:48.729
Or not.

01:22:48.731 --> 01:22:53.133
What kind of warlord
throws a pool party on a weekday?

01:22:53.135 --> 01:22:56.603
So... you wanna
say something?

01:22:56.605 --> 01:22:59.473
- Yeah.
- Okay. Say it.

01:22:59.475 --> 01:23:04.645
What is a beauty like you
doing with a goof like me?

01:23:07.249 --> 01:23:09.416
You never heard
of "a Merci fuck"?

01:23:09.418 --> 01:23:11.085
[ Horn Honks ]

01:23:11.921 --> 01:23:14.588
[ Honking ]

01:23:16.092 --> 01:23:18.158
May I ask you one favor?

01:23:20.329 --> 01:23:21.595
Okay.

01:23:21.597 --> 01:23:25.666
Don't do the Marilyn
wig thing with the scarves.

01:23:25.668 --> 01:23:28.102
Just save that for us.
I feel like that was our special deal.

01:23:28.104 --> 01:23:29.870
I will see you tomorrow.

01:23:29.872 --> 01:23:33.507
I have a lot of emotion
tied into it.

01:23:44.787 --> 01:23:48.522
[ Brian ] We are returning to the
picturesque Pashtun village.

01:23:48.524 --> 01:23:50.891
Although without backup.

01:23:50.893 --> 01:23:54.128
But this time
for twice my initial fee.

01:23:55.831 --> 01:23:58.065
You need a hook,
Mr. Bombay.

01:23:58.067 --> 01:24:01.101
There's a million
mercenary memoirs out there.

01:24:02.004 --> 01:24:04.405
I'm sorry.
This is what I do.

01:24:04.407 --> 01:24:07.474
Yeah. What you do
is talk shit.

01:24:07.476 --> 01:24:09.576
♪♪ [ Cell Phone: Ringtone ]

01:24:10.880 --> 01:24:14.648
I could get you
in a bidding situation.

01:24:14.650 --> 01:24:17.010
[ Riza ]
Miss Merci.

01:24:18.020 --> 01:24:19.753
House of pain.

01:24:19.755 --> 01:24:22.656
Me and this Pashtun girl,
we're in the hot tub with two guys.

01:24:22.658 --> 01:24:24.558
Oh, Lord.

01:24:24.560 --> 01:24:28.195
With Azam Ghol
and this... this Nizar.

01:24:28.197 --> 01:24:30.831
All right. Just give me
the gory details.

01:24:30.833 --> 01:24:32.566
<i>Richie, shut up.
Listen to me.</i>

01:24:32.568 --> 01:24:37.004
Those bullets that
you sold to Salima's father...

01:24:37.006 --> 01:24:39.106
I don't know
if they're, like, bad.

01:24:39.108 --> 01:24:40.741
They won't fire.
They're old.

01:24:40.743 --> 01:24:44.244
<i>Richie, it was all a setup.
Do you hear me?</i>

01:24:44.246 --> 01:24:46.547
<i>You delivered
the bad bullets for them.</i>

01:24:46.549 --> 01:24:49.283
<i>They used you, Richie.
You were the fucking patsy.</i>

01:24:49.285 --> 01:24:51.852
And Nizar's gonna kill Salima.
He's a crazy man.

01:24:51.854 --> 01:24:53.353
He kept screaming about it.

01:24:53.355 --> 01:24:55.222
She's, like, a whore,
an infidel, whatever.

01:24:55.224 --> 01:24:58.025
<i>And you put her on TV,
Richie.</i>

01:24:58.027 --> 01:25:00.360
They're gonna fucking kill her.
They're gonna kill her father,

01:25:00.362 --> 01:25:03.697
take over the village,
and you've got to do something.

01:25:03.699 --> 01:25:04.765
Do you get it?

01:25:06.702 --> 01:25:08.368
Thanks for the tip, honey.

01:25:08.370 --> 01:25:10.804
See you soon. Gotta go.

01:25:10.806 --> 01:25:13.807
Richie? Richie?

01:25:16.612 --> 01:25:18.378
Slight change of plans.

01:25:18.380 --> 01:25:20.380
Let's go back to Kabul.

01:25:20.983 --> 01:25:22.716
What?

01:25:22.718 --> 01:25:24.518
We're not gonna go get her?

01:25:28.591 --> 01:25:29.823
What?

01:25:29.825 --> 01:25:34.294
Your handshake is your word.
You shook her hand.

01:25:36.065 --> 01:25:39.466
You tell Salima
that your word is bond.

01:25:40.836 --> 01:25:42.469
Richie,

01:25:43.272 --> 01:25:45.305
you are her manager.

01:25:51.580 --> 01:25:53.180
Shit.

01:25:54.250 --> 01:25:57.317
Stop.
What?

01:25:57.319 --> 01:25:59.453
Just stop the car.

01:25:59.455 --> 01:26:01.722
Stop. Stop!

01:26:24.213 --> 01:26:26.280
[ Engine Stops ]

01:26:26.282 --> 01:26:29.216
Hey! The fuck?

01:26:30.853 --> 01:26:32.419
What's happening?

01:26:52.675 --> 01:26:54.308
What the hell?

01:27:01.984 --> 01:27:04.818
I never discovered Madonna.

01:27:04.820 --> 01:27:06.620
[ Riza ]
What?

01:27:08.324 --> 01:27:12.259
I never handled
a real headliner.

01:27:12.261 --> 01:27:16.597
I did have Eddie Money, but it was back
when he was Eddie Mahoney.

01:27:16.599 --> 01:27:19.566
It was long before
"Two Tickets To Paradise."

01:27:22.271 --> 01:27:24.338
I made a few bucks.

01:27:27.176 --> 01:27:30.410
I nailed a couple
of hot publicists.

01:27:31.513 --> 01:27:35.282
But I also gave up
a daughter I love.

01:27:39.088 --> 01:27:40.554
But, gentlemen,
Riza is right.

01:27:40.556 --> 01:27:45.592
There are four
sacred bonds in this life:

01:27:46.895 --> 01:27:48.762
a parent and child,

01:27:49.732 --> 01:27:51.598
a husband and wife,

01:27:52.434 --> 01:27:54.668
a priest and confessor...

01:27:57.306 --> 01:27:59.273
and manager-talent.

01:28:00.409 --> 01:28:02.075
What about doctor-patient?

01:28:02.077 --> 01:28:04.037
[ Riza ]
Or lawyer-client.

01:28:05.314 --> 01:28:06.880
Not sacred.

01:28:09.251 --> 01:28:12.319
[ Sighs ]
Now, Salima...

01:28:15.057 --> 01:28:16.890
is my act.

01:28:16.892 --> 01:28:18.558
She's mine.

01:28:19.828 --> 01:28:22.362
I am her manager.

01:28:23.465 --> 01:28:25.632
And my act needs me.

01:28:27.670 --> 01:28:29.303
Now.

01:28:57.266 --> 01:28:59.299
[ Speaking Pashto ]

01:28:59.301 --> 01:29:01.335
[ Riza ]
"You stole my daughter."

01:29:02.438 --> 01:29:05.472
Yes. But you raised her.
[ Riza Translating ]

01:29:05.474 --> 01:29:07.040
And you raised her...

01:29:07.042 --> 01:29:10.777
- to honor and celebrate...
- [ Riza Translating ]

01:29:10.779 --> 01:29:15.515
your family,
your country and your God.

01:29:15.517 --> 01:29:17.184
[ Riza Translating ]

01:29:17.186 --> 01:29:21.054
And if you didn't truly believe that,
wouldn't she be dead by now?

01:29:21.056 --> 01:29:22.856
[ Riza Translating ]

01:29:22.858 --> 01:29:24.791
[ Spits ]

01:29:25.461 --> 01:29:27.928
Hang on. It gets worse.

01:29:51.487 --> 01:29:53.387
[ Shouts In Pashto ]

01:29:56.091 --> 01:29:57.724
Understandable.

01:29:58.994 --> 01:30:00.761
We are your only chance.

01:30:02.164 --> 01:30:04.598
"We?"
Yeah.

01:30:04.600 --> 01:30:07.968
There is no "we."
I'm done with you.

01:30:09.505 --> 01:30:11.438
That's enough.

01:30:15.377 --> 01:30:18.745
When were you going to tell me?
Was it a big surprise or something?

01:30:18.747 --> 01:30:21.114
Something you were gonna
spring on me?

01:30:21.116 --> 01:30:22.816
It just hit me.

01:30:24.186 --> 01:30:26.887
This is your killer hook.

01:30:26.889 --> 01:30:32.526
This is your final chapter
of your best-selling book, right here.

01:30:32.528 --> 01:30:36.596
Oh, my book. My book.
You mean my posthumous book.

01:30:36.598 --> 01:30:38.865
The one that you're gonna make
all the money off of...

01:30:38.867 --> 01:30:41.735
after these guys shoot me
about a thousand times?

01:30:41.737 --> 01:30:44.137
There is no deal, Hollywood.
[ Richie ] All right. All right.

01:30:44.139 --> 01:30:45.739
I never do this.

01:30:45.741 --> 01:30:48.975
If you ever tell anyone I did this,
I'll deny it.

01:30:48.977 --> 01:30:50.944
But I'm gonna cut my fee.

01:30:50.946 --> 01:30:53.980
There'll be no Richie 35
on this one.

01:30:53.982 --> 01:30:58.151
There'll be Richie 15,
and we're still both gonna do great.

01:30:58.153 --> 01:31:02.456
Because this is golden.

01:31:04.493 --> 01:31:08.161
Brian, you don't
wanna be the guy...

01:31:09.431 --> 01:31:12.165
that left the Alamo.

01:31:18.574 --> 01:31:20.740
You are a piece of work.

01:31:21.910 --> 01:31:23.477
Thank you.

01:31:23.479 --> 01:31:27.180
My posthumous book...
I wonder what you'll call it.

01:31:27.182 --> 01:31:29.483
Chief, this is for you.

01:31:29.485 --> 01:31:31.184
[ Riza Speaks Dari ]
[ Brian Speaks Dari ]

01:31:31.186 --> 01:31:35.255
In that truck is all the ammunition
you will ever need.

01:31:35.257 --> 01:31:39.025
- [ Riza Translating ]
- And <i> my</i> bullets work.

01:31:39.027 --> 01:31:43.630
- Now come on back here with me.
- [ Riza Translating ]

01:31:43.632 --> 01:31:45.632
[ Chattering In Pashto ]

01:31:45.634 --> 01:31:49.102
[ Brian ] That's for you. Brand new.
There you go.

01:31:49.104 --> 01:31:50.837
Careful with that.

01:32:06.355 --> 01:32:10.090
[ Chattering In Pashto ]

01:32:22.404 --> 01:32:25.472
[ Woman Speaking Pashto ]

01:32:25.474 --> 01:32:28.708
[ Man Speaking Pashto ]

01:32:41.857 --> 01:32:45.325
- Thanks for not killing me.
- [ Riza Translating ]

01:32:45.327 --> 01:32:47.027
[ Speaking Pashto ]

01:32:47.029 --> 01:32:50.630
What did he say?
The day is not over yet.

01:32:52.568 --> 01:32:54.134
Pretty good.

01:33:01.443 --> 01:33:04.744
[ Wind Whistling ]

01:33:13.188 --> 01:33:14.788
Richie.

01:33:16.024 --> 01:33:17.624
Hi.

01:33:22.798 --> 01:33:26.900
In all the excitement,
I forgot to congratulate you.

01:33:26.902 --> 01:33:29.269
[ Salima Chuckles ]
You won.

01:33:29.271 --> 01:33:31.871
I told you.

01:33:31.873 --> 01:33:34.074
Yeah.

01:33:34.076 --> 01:33:36.209
And that was nothing.

01:33:36.211 --> 01:33:39.813
I had a killer arrangement
for the finals.

01:33:39.815 --> 01:33:42.749
Strings. Gospel choir.

01:33:42.751 --> 01:33:45.719
Wall of sound. Huge.

01:33:45.721 --> 01:33:47.954
You would have won in a walk.

01:33:53.762 --> 01:33:59.065
Salima, honey,
you were the best I ever heard.

01:34:02.270 --> 01:34:03.970
You saw it all.

01:34:05.007 --> 01:34:09.009
Well...
[ Chuckles ] Except for this part.

01:34:09.011 --> 01:34:14.180
Richie, this, right now...
This will be the best part.

01:34:14.750 --> 01:34:16.349
The dying part?

01:34:16.351 --> 01:34:21.121
[ Chuckles ] Not the dying part.
The living.

01:34:21.123 --> 01:34:23.757
You... You folks
from the mystic East...

01:34:23.759 --> 01:34:28.194
have a much better handle
on the whole karma, life/death thing.

01:34:29.097 --> 01:34:32.098
Rumi writes,

01:34:32.100 --> 01:34:36.169
"There's a candle in your heart,
ready to be kindled.

01:34:36.171 --> 01:34:41.174
There's a void in your soul,
ready to be filled.

01:34:41.810 --> 01:34:43.943
You feel it, don't you?"

01:34:43.945 --> 01:34:47.447
Richie.
You will.

01:34:47.449 --> 01:34:49.115
I...

01:34:49.117 --> 01:34:52.252
I promise
you will feel it.

01:35:00.562 --> 01:35:04.698
<i>♪♪ [ Vocalizing ]</i>

01:35:07.736 --> 01:35:11.938
<i>♪♪ [ Vocalizing Continues ]</i>

01:35:14.509 --> 01:35:17.210
<i>[ Man ]
♪ Mama, take this badge off of me ♪</i>

01:35:21.483 --> 01:35:25.051
<i>♪ I can't use it anymore ♪</i>

01:35:28.156 --> 01:35:31.991
<i>♪ It's getting dark,
too dark to see ♪</i>

01:35:35.030 --> 01:35:39.099
<i>♪ I feel I'm knocking
on heaven's door ♪</i>

01:35:42.070 --> 01:35:46.072
<i>♪ Knock, knock, knocking
on heaven's door ♪</i>

01:35:48.944 --> 01:35:53.079
<i>♪ Knock, knock, knocking
on heaven's door ♪</i>

01:35:56.017 --> 01:36:00.086
<i>♪ Knock, knock, knocking
on heaven's door ♪</i>

01:36:02.924 --> 01:36:06.793
<i>♪ Knock, knock, knocking
on heaven's door ♪♪</i>

01:36:11.133 --> 01:36:12.499
This is nuts!

01:36:14.936 --> 01:36:18.371
I'm not a fighter.
I'm a deal maker.

01:36:18.373 --> 01:36:20.874
I'm gonna go make a deal.

01:36:20.876 --> 01:36:22.942
You just gotta love this guy.

01:36:25.814 --> 01:36:27.881
[ Chuckles ]

01:36:27.883 --> 01:36:31.117
These guys have no idea
what they're up against.

01:36:32.287 --> 01:36:34.220
Let me do the talking.

01:36:35.257 --> 01:36:36.956
Knock yourself out.

01:36:48.436 --> 01:36:51.404
- [ Tariq Speaks Pashto ]
- [ Riza ] "What are you doing?"

01:36:51.406 --> 01:36:54.607
I'm representing.
I'm here to negotiate.

01:36:54.609 --> 01:36:57.477
And you?
[ Speaking Pashto ]

01:36:58.814 --> 01:37:02.482
"We are here to kill all unbelievers
and the whore who sings."

01:37:05.420 --> 01:37:08.021
Okay. I'm hearing you.

01:37:08.023 --> 01:37:11.491
More of a deal breaker
than a negotiation.

01:37:11.493 --> 01:37:15.829
Let's get serious. What's it gonna
take for all of this to go away?

01:37:15.831 --> 01:37:19.098
[ Speaking Pashto ]

01:37:19.100 --> 01:37:21.701
[ Riza ]
"Kill him. Kill this fool now."

01:37:21.703 --> 01:37:27.807
Okay. Very quickly.
A key is to know what the other guy wants.

01:37:27.809 --> 01:37:32.445
You are a warlord.
You want war, I suppose.

01:37:32.447 --> 01:37:35.014
Money. Power.
Maybe opium.

01:37:35.016 --> 01:37:37.617
And in an ideal world...

01:37:37.619 --> 01:37:43.389
you'd like CIA and Taliban to both
pay you to sell out your own country.

01:37:43.391 --> 01:37:44.958
You're a warlord.

01:37:48.463 --> 01:37:51.130
[ Gunfire Continues ]

01:37:59.908 --> 01:38:03.009
[ Brian ]
Stand down! Stand down!

01:38:03.011 --> 01:38:06.312
[ Men Shouting In Pashto ]

01:38:07.482 --> 01:38:10.483
Anybody else wanna see
how real bullets work?

01:38:10.485 --> 01:38:11.985
Richie, you're all right.

01:38:11.987 --> 01:38:14.587
It's a flesh wound.
Walk it off. Let's go.

01:38:18.760 --> 01:38:22.028
<i>♪♪ [ Vocalizing ]</i>

01:38:22.030 --> 01:38:24.931
<i>[ Salima ]
♪ Now I've been happy lately ♪</i>

01:38:24.933 --> 01:38:28.067
<i>♪ Thinking about
the good things to come ♪</i>

01:38:28.069 --> 01:38:31.337
<i>♪ And I believe it could be ♪</i>

01:38:31.339 --> 01:38:33.706
<i>♪ Something good has begun ♪</i>

01:38:33.708 --> 01:38:37.510
<i>♪ Oh, I've been smiling lately ♪</i>

01:38:37.512 --> 01:38:40.013
♪ Dreaming about the world
